name: The Lost Souls 👻
description:
"The Lost Souls" by BryantW

We are all lost souls in a world that doesn't care for our existence. A Dream. A Flow of Contentiousness. A River that will find its end.

This artwork was created using old public domain illustrations collage together and remixed with patterns and other effects in Photoshop.
